{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act12side", "eventName": "多索雷斯假日", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DH-9", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "鼠膽龍威", "storyInfo": "在陳的吸引注意下，林雨霞成功救出船上的人質。\n另一邊，陳已然無路可退，千鈞一髮之際，林雨霞開船趕到。同時，遊輪爆炸。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G06", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 10, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "進展順利，我快摸到餐廳了。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "？！", "name": "陳"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又見面了，陳小姐。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你該好好躺在那。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也想這麼做，最好我睜眼之後，無論勝敗，這件事都結束了。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜，我不能這麼做。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你打不過我的。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我現在越來越慶幸自己一開始將你們當做最大的敵人來對待了......如果我沒有這麼做，計畫可能無法走到這一步。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......不像是那種狂熱分子，為什麼一定要做這樣的事？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事到如今，讓我說說我真實的想法吧。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坎黛拉女士曾經說過，她的父親，這座城市的前市長，一個被萊塔尼亞政府扶持，除了貪污什麼都不會做的廢物。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在被憤怒的市民們踢開辦公室的門前，帶著妻子和女兒逃離了這個國家。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的父親雖然作為人是個徹頭徹尾的垃圾，但是作為這個人渣的女兒，她跟著父親先去了卡西米爾，然後去了維多利亞。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟著父親，她知道了金錢的用法，更知道了錢的意義。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後她回到了這座城市，並成為了這裡的市長。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在反抗軍一事無成的時候，這座城市已經能夠生產出全玻利瓦爾最好的酒、咖啡，還有糖。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多索雷斯的龍舌蘭，在萊塔尼亞和哥倫比亞都能喝到。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在萊塔尼亞和哥倫比亞勾心鬥角的時候，這座城市成為了兩邊的貴族都會選擇的度假勝地。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們甚至還要遵循坎黛拉女士的規則，不能在這裡動手。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而讓他們甘願這麼做的，不是武力，不是刀劍法術，是金錢、娛樂和奢侈品。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是這座城市光鮮的外皮。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道我不該這麼想。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我無法阻止自己去這麼想——", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在某種意義上來講，從結果上來說，是不是坎黛拉女士比我父親要更熱愛玻利瓦爾這個國家？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他只是在盲目地追求著國家這個意象，他想要一個名叫玻利瓦爾的國家。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它的領土是它作為附屬地時被決定的大小，它的人民是一直以來生活在這裡的人民。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後呢？這個國家如何面對哥倫比亞和萊塔尼亞的傾軋？這個國家如何作為一個國家發展下去？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不知道。他其實不知道玻利瓦爾會是一個怎樣的國家。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而坎黛拉女士至少找到了一條路，她看到了它存在的意義，並打算讓這種意義成為現實。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......歪理邪說。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好過空口白話，不是嗎？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然如此為什麼你還要協助你的父親？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為我自出生起就看著我父親在戰火裡打滾，看著他從意氣風發逐漸變得沉默寡言。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#6"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道我的父親是個怎樣的人，他和那些已經選擇了屈服於時代的人不一樣。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#6"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使在坎黛拉女士手下做事讓我產生了一些念頭，也不意味著我就要背叛我的父親。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#6"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我也無法否認，這些念頭越來越強烈，以至於讓我逐漸開始思考一些別的可能性。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我將這次計畫作為一個分界點。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會全心全意協助父親，如果他成功了，那我就協助他。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果他失敗了，那我也將接受自己的改變，成為坎黛拉女士的擁躉。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，如果我死了——", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就是死了，哈哈。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而現在，還不到結束的時候。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我不會讓你過去的。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......既然如此，那就沒什麼好說的了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，認識你很高興，陳小姐。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不是在這種情況下認識，我還挺想好好帶著你和林小姐認識一下這座城市的。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "免了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想也是。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G01", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$frontline_intro", "key": "$frontline_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_020"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "B隊，來幾個人，跟我走。", "name": "船長護衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_020"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_193", "name2": "avg_npc_193", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "遲鈍的潘喬手下"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_193"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_193", "name2": "avg_npc_193", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像是比賽裡那個特別能打的鼠膽龍威隊，裡面那個姓陳的女俠好像還在反抗。", "name": "機靈的潘喬手下"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_193"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_193", "name2": "avg_npc_193", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船上都是我們的人，其他不是的參賽選手也都在這了，她怎麼反抗？", "name": "遲鈍的潘喬手下"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_193"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_193", "name2": "avg_npc_193", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她好像把埃內斯托給放倒了。", "name": "機靈的潘喬手下"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_193"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後在船上上躥下跳的，船長都已經親自去抓她了。", "name": "機靈的潘喬手下"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_193"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖嘖，真是厲害。之前埃內斯托說不能小看她們，我還不信。", "name": "機靈的潘喬手下"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_193"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_193", "name2": "avg_npc_193", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？這麼一說，那個姓林的女俠呢？", "name": "遲鈍的潘喬手下"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_193"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我好像也沒在這些人質裡看到。", "name": "遲鈍的潘喬手下"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_193"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_193", "name2": "avg_npc_193", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰知道，跳海跑了吧。", "name": "機靈的潘喬手下"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_193"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在這。", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_193"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "？！", "name": "遲鈍的潘喬手下"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_193"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "ypos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fan", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_193", "name2": "avg_npc_193", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_193", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "林雨霞從兩人頭頂的天花板跳下，兩記手刀解決了兩人。"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_193"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快，圍住她！", "name": "警覺的潘喬手下"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_193"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（陳暉潔吸引注意力的本事還不錯，人數不算多。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（速戰速決吧。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "面對房間內幾名守衛的包圍，只見林雨霞微微欠身，不退反進。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 750.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$sheildimpact", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "第一人，被一記膝撞接一腳，撞到第二人身上，兩人一起狠狠衝撞到柱子上，柱子幾乎被撞斷，兩人暈厥。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 750.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$knifegore", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "第三人正欲揮動武器，卻發現自己手臂上有兩道血絲，而後慘叫出聲，跪倒在地，被一記手刀送入黑暗。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 750.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bottlebroken", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "第四人與第五人想要聯手進攻，卻只見林雨霞腿一抬，一張餐桌連帶上面的餐具向他們飛來，還來不及反應，已被放倒在地。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 750.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "第六人見勢不妙，拿起對講機想要傳達情報，卻發現對講機不知何時已經冒起了煙，而後渾身一輕，發現自己已經身處半空之中，劃過一道美麗的弧線，墜入海中。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 750.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "本就擅長短兵相接的林雨霞，在狹窄的餐廳中將自己的優勢發揮得淋漓盡致，電光火石之間就解決了餐廳裡看管人質們的守衛。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 750.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "而人質們，也就是被船長綁架的權貴們以及被捲入的一些參賽選手，則縮在餐廳的一角，面帶驚疑地看著她。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 750.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不想死就跟我走。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼逃，船上都是潘喬這渣滓的手下！", "name": "權貴"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們幾個。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_204", "name2": "avg_npc_205", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噫，噫——", "name": "軟弱的參賽選手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_204"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_204", "name2": "avg_npc_205", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別丟人了，站起來。", "name": "不屈的參賽選手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_205"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_205", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "林女俠，我們聽你的。", "name": "不屈的參賽選手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_205"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_205", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來打前鋒，你們保護好這些老爺。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_205", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "懂了。", "name": "不屈的參賽選手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_205"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼......", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惡，來晚了嗎......", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃內斯托說你會在這裡，果然沒錯。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（埃內斯托......被陳暉潔解決後醒過來馬上就判明了狀況嗎。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（是個人才，可惜了。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（而且，這個小妹妹，沒想到在這裡又遇到了她。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小妹妹，你不應該參與這種事。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我叫拉菲艾拉，不是小妹妹。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是爸爸的養女，所以我應該參與才對。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哥哥說過，你是好人，為什麼你要阻撓我們？", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "jump", "power": 0.0, "times": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "jump", "xpos": 100.0, "power": 0.0, "times": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "false", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得自己在做一件好事嗎？", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不是很清楚，但是哥哥和爸爸都說這座城市很壞，我聽他們的。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你應該有自己的主見，小妹妹。有的時候，長輩是需要晚輩幫助的。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們有著自己的經驗，也會拘泥於自己的經驗。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而當你接過他們的班時，你不能只走他們的老路。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要用你的思考去打破他們的陳規，你要思考只有你才能做的事。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 282, 