tes": {"content": "聽不懂。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，但你可以稍微記一下。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，我還有些額外的事要做，所以，到了好孩子該睡覺的時間了，小妹妹。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G06", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（嘖，林雨霞這個女人，剛才忽然掛掉了電話，再打也打不通，她在幹什麼？！）", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$phonevibration", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_npc_196_1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#6"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "林雨霞，你在搞什麼，我二十分鐘前就聽到你救走了人質的消息，現在他們大部分都去追你了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#6"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#6"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，我現在不在人質身邊，他們應該已經逃出去了。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#6"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#4"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你到底......", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#4"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#4"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相信我。你現在來底層，我們一起......", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#4"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "？！", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳倏地放下手機，轉過頭去，潘喬和他的手下們正站在不遠處。"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#4"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一直聽說龍門的總督魏彥吾是個了不起的傢伙。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#4"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果他送來的兩個人，厲害倒是挺厲害，腦子卻不清楚。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#4"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，魏彥吾和坎黛拉也是一路貨色。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#4"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#6"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#6"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#4"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們這種眼裡只有錢，腦子裡只有享樂的人，我真是恨不得把你們殺得一乾二淨。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#4"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道你們龍門是怎麼樣的，但是自我出生起，這個國家每時每刻都在流血。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#4"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰他媽不想握握手就把日子過好了，可是誰都他媽的做不到。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#6"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我告訴你，流再多的血，也沒有這座城市一天吸得多！", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#6"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，我沒空陪你玩遊戲了。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#4"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1", "name2": "avg_npc_192_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要嘛乖乖投降，要嘛你就給我死在這裡。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#6"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（為什麼你要這麼做？你真的認為自己正確嗎？即使這麼做會流許多的血？）", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（這些問題......毫無意義。）", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（在他眼中，我就是那個阻礙他的人，而我——）", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（我無法反駁他。）", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（這並不是因為我對自己的行為產生後悔。）", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（而是我在瞭解了潘喬的行為動機後，對他並不是沒有認同。）", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（即使我依然否定他的做法。）", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（但我不夠瞭解玻利瓦爾，我不夠瞭解戰爭，我無法給出一個更好的方法。）", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（所以我無法反駁他。）", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（我也無法在此時拔劍。）", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（赤霄斷然不會認同現在的我，我明白。）", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（那麼，我該做的是——）", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳緩緩舉起手中的銃。"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#6", "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你選擇死亡。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#6"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潘喬緩緩舉起手中鐵錨。"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而就在此時——"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跳，陳暉潔。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "char_empty"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_1013_spchen_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "陳來不及多想，就從甲板上一躍而下。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 750.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$motorbikestart", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.1, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而在下面等待她的，是林雨霞駕駛的小船。"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，給我追！", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}